DialogueNode.dialogue: Hi, I wanted to introduce myself! I'm Alex, the new HR hire.
Oh, hi Alex! It's nice to meet you. I'm Sharon.
It's great to meet you too, Sharon! What do you do here?
I'm a programmer, but at this point it feels like my job is reminding people that I'm not a secretary.
...Thanks for not assuming that I was, by the way.
Oh, wow. I would never assume that! I'm so sorry that happens.
Wow, I can't believe people do that! That's infuriating!
Haha it's okay, it was a joke, not an HR complaint. Don't worry. I really enjoy it here.
Well, I should probably get back to work now. But it was nice meeting you, Alex. I hope you can make a real difference around here.
Oh, of course. It was nice meeting you, too.
(I wonder what she meant with that last comment? Is there that much that needs changing?)
